          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "仙佛修持理自通，个中妙用本无穷。花开花谢天中日，云去云来岭上峰。"
        },
        {
          "character": "清风、明月",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我二人乃万寿山五庄观镇元大仙座前两个道童，清风，明月是也。只因师父被\n元始天尊邀去上清弥罗宫，讲混元道果。说有故人唐三藏，原来佛家第二徒弟。\n五百年前，在盂兰会上相识。他今奉唐王圣旨，往西天拜佛求经。从此经过。\n命将人参果两枚，奉敬唐三藏。要防他跟随的啰唣。只得在此伺候。正是："
        },
        {
          "character": "清风、明月",
          "line_type": "同念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "清虚人事少，寂寞道心生。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（清风、明月同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [],
      "stats": {
        "line_counts": {
          "stage_direction": 4,
          "同念": 1
        },
        "singing_ratio": 0.0,
        "dominant_style_family": null,
        "musical_styles": []
      }
    },
    {
      "scene_index": 3,
      "label": "第三场",
      "characters_present": [
        "世上哪有结人树",
        "唐僧",
        "孙悟空",
        "家师临行吩咐去",
        "明月",
        "沙悟净",
        "清风",
        "猪悟能"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（孙悟空、猪悟能、沙悟净、唐僧同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "唐僧",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "晓风吹月影，"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "曙色映霞光。"
        },
        {
          "character": "猪悟能",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "路远心偏急，"
        },
        {
          "character": "沙悟净",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "人饿走谩荒。"
        },
        {
          "character": "唐僧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "今日天色尚早，略向道旁稍歇一回，再行如何？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "途路甚远，只好随走随歇。莫论早晚，也要趱路。"
        },
        {
          "character": "唐僧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "徒弟，前面一座高山，看这光景，与别处不同。定是平安去处，料也没有什么\n凶险。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "师父，平安也要走，凶险也要行。且到那里，便知分晓。"
        },
        {
          "character": "唐僧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "看此山光景，大约相连雷音。好生整肃端严也。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "早得紧哩。"
        },
        {
          "character": "沙悟净",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大师兄。我们要到雷音，还有多少路程？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "若论我，一日可也走得五十遭。"
        },
        {
          "character": "猪悟能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "走一百遭，有谁看见？空说这样大话！"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "若论师父，休想。"
        },
        {
          "character": "唐僧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "依你说几时方到呢？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你自小走到老，老了又小，也还难到。只要见性诚，回首即是灵山。"
        },
        {
          "character": "唐僧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "悟空说得是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "师父，那松篁深处，楼阁巍峨，定是福地灵区，名山古寺。"
        },
        {
          "character": "唐僧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有此大业林。理宜参谒。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请师父下马。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（清风、明月自下场门同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "清风、明月",
          "line_type": "同念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "万寿山福地，五庄观洞天。"
        },
        {
          "character": "清风、明月",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老师父。失迎了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "唐僧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "贫僧稽首。"
        },
        {
          "character": "清风、明月",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "师父请进。"
        },
        {
          "character": "唐僧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请尊师出来拜见。"
        },
        {
          "character": "清风、明月",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "家师往弥罗宫去了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "唐僧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "仙童，你这五庄观，实乃西方仙界。为何不供三清四帝，罗天诸宰，只供天地\n二字的牌位？"
        },
        {
          "character": "清风、明月",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不瞒老师父说，这两个字，还当得起供养，余者都受不起香火的。"
        },
        {
          "character": "唐僧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "为何呢？"
        },
        {
          "character": "清风、明月",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三清是家师的朋友，四帝是家师的故人。九矅之神，都是家师的晚辈。"
        },
        {
          "character": "唐僧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "原来有这个缘故。你们去安顿行李马匹。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（孙悟空、猪悟能、沙悟净同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "唐僧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请问令师的法号？"
        },
        {
          "character": "清风",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "家师道号镇元子。"
        },
        {
          "character": "唐僧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "原来如此。"
        },
        {
          "character": "清风",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "师弟取茶来。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（明月下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "清风",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请问老师可是大唐差往西天取经的三藏法师么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "唐僧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不敢，贫僧正是。仙童何以知我贱名？"
        },
        {
          "character": "清风",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "家师临行，曾吩咐弟子们。老师父请少待，待弟子取仙果奉献。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（清风下，明月捧茶上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "明月",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老师父请茶。"
        },
        {
          "character": "唐僧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "生受了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（清风捧果上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "清风",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "师父，我这里山荒地僻之处，无物为敬。特献素果两枚，权为解渴充饥。"
        },
        {
          "character": "唐僧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "阿弥陀佛。这是三朝未满的孩童，如何解渴充饥？"
        },
        {
          "character": "清风、明月",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "师父。这叫作人参果。是树上结的。"
        },
        {
          "character": "唐僧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "岂有此理！树上怎会结起人来？快请拿过了。仙童，你我出家人呵！"
        },
        {
          "character": "唐僧",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "承蒙献果理应取，\n怎用人身来充饥？\n惹得贫僧心又疑。"
        },
        {
          "character": "世上哪有结人树、清风、明月",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老师父。"
        },
        {
          "character": "世上哪有结人树、清风、明月",
          "line_type": "同唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "尊声师父莫称奇，\n此果本是树上的。\n日精月华莫负伊。"
        },
        {
          "character": "家师临行吩咐去、唐僧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "阿弥陀佛。贫僧再不敢吃此物，这是我的福缘浅薄。"
        },
        {
          "character": "清风、明月",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请师父到前边客堂用斋罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "唐僧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这倒使得。"
        },
        {
          "character": "唐僧",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "若爱口头甜，冤愆定难免。"
        },
        {
          "character": "清风、明月",
          "line_type": "同念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "当面错良缘，皆因根行浅。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
