    {
      "scene_index": 5,
      "label": "第五场",
      "characters_present": [
        "唐僧",
        "孙悟空",
        "明月",
        "沙悟净",
        "清风",
        "猪悟能"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（清风、明月同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "清风",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不好了。师弟，我二人奉师父法旨，看守人参果树，并接唐僧到来。谁想被他"
        },
        {
          "character": "明月",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "师父原叫我们防他徒弟罗唣，如今果应其言了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "清风",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我和你先去告诉他师父，看他如何处分。"
        },
        {
          "character": "明月",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有理。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（唐僧上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "唐僧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二位道兄，为何如此惊慌？"
        },
        {
          "character": "清风",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三藏师父，了不得。你令徒将我观中人参果盗去了三枚。我们师父回来，定不"
        },
        {
          "character": "唐僧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "只怕没有此事。"
        },
        {
          "character": "清风",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好个糊涂的和尚。我们告诉你，你到如此索然。敢是纵容徒弟，作此无耻之事"
        },
        {
          "character": "唐僧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二位言重。"
        },
        {
          "character": "清风",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "住了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "清风",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "听你言来假不知，"
        },
        {
          "character": "唐僧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二位，非是贫僧纵容徒弟，我实在不知其故。还仗二位周全。"
        },
        {
          "character": "清风",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好。装聋作哑，反倒叫我们周全。"
        },
        {
          "character": "唐僧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有这等事，待我换他们出来。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（孙悟空、猪悟能、沙悟净同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "沙悟净",
          "line_type": "同唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "闻听呼唤似雷霆，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（孙悟空、猪悟能、沙悟净同见。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "唐僧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "徒弟们，你们又惹祸了。是何缘故，窃取他家的人参果，尔等可好好与他分辩。"
        },
        {
          "character": "猪悟能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不好了，人参果的事发了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你这蠢呆子，不用多言。"
        },
        {
          "character": "清风",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好大话。你这馋痨，偷吃了我家仙果，还亏你公然自认。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我到你观中，你是主人。既有仙果，摘来献客才是。为何躲在房中，你二人拿"
        },
        {
          "character": "明月",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你做了贼，倒说我拿贼的不是。世上哪里有这样歹人！"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "胡说！"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "蠢童休要乱胡为，"
        },
        {
          "character": "清风",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好厉害的贼寇。我们快去报与师父知道。"
        },
        {
          "character": "清风",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一心忙似箭，两脚走如飞。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（清风、明月同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "猪悟能",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不好了。他们跑去，报知他们师父，定要惹气了。这便怎么处。这却不管我事"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我把你这呆子，谁像你这等干净。"
        },
        {
          "character": "沙悟净",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "恐怕他们师父回来，定要歪缠哪。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不妨。你二人快去收拾行李马匹，请师父起行。待我前去拔了他的树木，索性"
        },
        {
          "character": "孙悟空",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "行囊打叠前途会，"
        },
        {
          "character": "沙悟净",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二哥。都是你起的祸端。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。孙悟空上，拔树，下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（完）"
        }
      ],
